TaskService --> CrmDbContext
UserProvisioningService --> CrmDbContext
UserQueryService --> CrmDbContext
UserManagementService --> CrmDbContext
RecommendationDataSeedHelper --> CrmDbContext

UserProvisioningService --> IKeycloakAdminService
UserManagementService --> IKeycloakAdminService
AuthService --> IKeycloakAdminService

KeycloakAdminService ..|> IKeycloakAdminService
CrmDbContext --> BaseEntity
CrmDbContext --> User
